ALTA — Next Generation Crypto Trading &
Learning Platform
Project Overview
Version 1.0 | June 2026
Executive Summary
ALTA is an ambitious next-generation platform that aims to surpass TradingView in the
cryptocurrency space by combining powerful real-time charting, news aggregation,
paper trading, and comprehensive trading education into one beautifully designed
application.
Our mission is to make professional-grade crypto trading accessible, educational, and
visually stunning for beginners and experienced traders alike.
Problem
• Existing platforms (TradingView, CoinMarketCap, DexScreener) are fragmented.
• New traders lack integrated education and safe practice environments.
• Many tools have outdated or cluttered interfaces.
Solution
ALTA provides an all-in-one beautiful ecosystem:
• Superior modern UI/UX with focus on visual excellence
• Real-time advanced charting
• Integrated demo (paper) trading accounts
• Structured learning academy with progress tracking
• News aggregator and sentiment overview
• Portfolio tracker with wallet connection
Unique Value Proposition
• Best-in-class Visual Design — modern, dark, premium feel
• Deep integration of Education + Practice directly in the trading interface
• Future Web3 features (on-chain analytics, copy-trading, token economy)
• Freemium model with strong community focus
Target Audience
• Crypto beginners wanting to learn trading
• Intermediate and advanced traders
• DeFi users and portfolio managers
MVP Features
1. Landing page & authentication
2. Real-time multi-symbol charts (Lightweight Charts)
3. Top coins list with search
4. News aggregator
5. Paper trading simulator
6. Basic education section (articles + quizzes)
7. Portfolio tracker
Technology Stack
• Frontend: Next.js 15, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
• Charts: TradingView Lightweight Charts
• Database & Auth: Supabase (free tier)
• APIs: CoinGecko, CCXT
• Hosting: Vercel + Supabase
Monetization
• Freemium (Pro subscription for advanced features)
• Affiliate partnerships with exchanges
• Sponsored educational content
• Future token/utility model
Roadmap
• Q3 2026: MVP Launch
• Q4 2026: Wallet integration + advanced education
• 2027: AI analytics, community features, mobile app
Team
Bootstrapped by passionate founder with strong design focus. Open to co-founders and contributors 